                        <div>
                            <h2>Safe, welcoming and full of culture</h2>
                            <p>Belfast is home. It’s a city that welcomes you with open arms. From the moment you arrive, you’re a part of its community. It’s Northern Ireland’s capital city - over a third of all people living in Northern Ireland live in Belfast. It’s safe and quiet, yet buzzing with events and culture.</p>
                            <p>The Titanic was built right here in Belfast. You’ll find snippets of history across the city with castles, monasteries and incredible architecture. It’s surrounded by natural beauty too, including Northern Ireland’s dramatic coastline with beautiful beaches to explore.</p>
                            <a href="/en/universities/queens-university-belfast/courses" class="l-cta cta">Find a course in Belfast</a>
